sentences.english: Chandler: If can invade Poland, there isn't anything I can't do.

sentences.english: Excuse me now. Talk to my men if you want anything.
sentences.chinese: 我有啲事走先，有啲乜嘢需要同我手下讲得啦。

sentences.english: Long since my junior I came across the best English teacher.
sentences.chinese: 唔知道应该拿乜嘢来报答我的英语老师。

sentences.english: Young Miss, how did you make it tamed?
sentences.chinese: 小女士，妳究竟用乜嘢方法驯服呢只野兽？
